******************************************************************************************

Functionality:-

Used Data Structure Dictionary to store the words where keys are the words and values are the frequency for each word. Performed operations on this dictionary to get the vocabulary 
size, unique words, eliminating stop_words.

Functions:-

def total_words():-  summing the frequency i.e the value of each key in the dictionary
def unique_words():- calculating the total number of keys in the dictionary which is actually the unique word count.
def top_20_words1():- sorting the dictionary based on value (frequency) in descending order so that we get highest frequency words and looping till 20 to get the top 20 ranked words


